CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 19, 1954, pg. 8 reads: "Thousands Attend Courier Home, Food Show...3. "All" Detergent Booth was represented by Miss Becky Bakos who did the straight part in the "All" skit entitled, "No Soap Opera," Mrs. Jean Kelleher and Mr. Weiser (not shown)...Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Becky Bakos and Jean Kelleher standing in All Detergent Monsanto Chemical Co. booth in Hunt Armory for the 1954 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
